param.value: A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to perform its role and is part of a scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to perform one of the support roles within in a water utility.

A grouping / linking of major corporate support functions that enable the core business services to be provided for each of the types of business product schemes. This covers the corporate support functions which support more than one operational schemes and operational management area (district).

A grouping / linking of major operational support functions that enable the core business services to be provided for each of the types of business product schemes. This covers the operational support functions which support schemes that are managed by one operational management area (district).
A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to collect or transfer raw water and is part of a Supply Scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to collect or transfer raw water and is part of a Potable Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Potable Water Source) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to collect and transfer raw water and is part of a Supply Scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to collect or transfer raw water and is part of a Non-Potable Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Non Potable Source) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to collect and transfer raw water and is part of a Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Irrigation Source / Non Potable Source) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to collect and transfer irrigation water as part of a Supply Scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role (Water Source) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to collect and transfer reuse water and is part of a Supply Scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to collect product and transfer from customers and is part of a Collection Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Wastewater Collection) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to collect and transfer wastewater from customers and is part of a Collection Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Drainage Collection) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to collect stormwater and transfer from customers and is part of a Collection Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to treat product to a required standard and can be part of a supply or Collection Scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to treat product to required standards and is part of Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Water Treatment) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to treat raw water to potable standards and is part of Supply Scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to treat product to required standards as part of Non-Potable Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Non-Potable Water Treatment) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to treat raw water to required standards and is part of Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Water Treatment) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to treat reuse water to potable standards and is part of Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Irrigation Water Treatment) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to treat raw water to required standards and is part of Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Wastewater Treatment) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to treat wastewater to disposal standards and is part of a Collection Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Drainage Treatment) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to treat stormwater to disposal standards and is part of a Collection Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to transfer product to the environment as part of the disposal part of a Collection Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Wastewater Disposal) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to transfer treated wastewater products (liquids and solids) to customers (i.e. Reuse) or the environment and is part of a Collection Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Drainage Disposal) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to transfer stormwater (liquids and solids) to the environment and is part of a Collection Scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role in the utility's service chain and contains all the components necessary to deliver product to customers and is part of a Supply Scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to deliver product to customers and is part of a Potable Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Potable Water Distribution) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to deliver potable water to customers and is part of a Supply Scheme.
A major stage that has a specific role in the water utility service chain and contains all the components necessary to deliver product to customers and is part of a Non-Potable Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Non Potable Distribution) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to deliver non potable water to customers and is part of a Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Irrigation Distribution / Non Potable Distribution) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to deliver irrigation water to customers and is part of a Supply Scheme.

A major stage that has a specific role (Non-Potable Water Distribution) in the water utility service chain. It contains all the components necessary to deliver reuse water to customers and is part of a Supply Scheme.
